{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "万马堂大旗重在烈日下飘扬，马芳铃为父亲马空群向傅红雪求情，甚至愿随他离去，却被傅红雪以“为父亲还是为自己”逼问后离开。街心另一边，路小佳在热水桶中等雇主和目标，丁灵琳与叶开故意用斗嘴激怒他，却被他冷静识破。叶开看出路小佳能忍，丁灵琳也与叶开关系更近。胡掌柜继续催局，路小佳反而察觉这些雇主底细可疑。最后马芳铃主动来到街心，承认自己就是路小佳要的女人，忍辱接下擦背布，暗示要路小佳杀死傅红雪，路小佳淡然保证目标活不长。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我知道你心里在想什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你心里一定在想，总有一天要将这面大旗砍倒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是你永远砍不倒的！永远！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以我劝你，还是赶快走，走得越远越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你知道我要砍的并不是那面旗，是马空群的头！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你为什么要这样恨他？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是你也永远打不倒他的，他远比你强得多，你根本比不上他！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你知道我一定可以杀了他的，他已经老了，太老了，老得已只能流血。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，他已老了，已只不过是个无能为力的老头子，所以你就算杀了他对你也没什么好处。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你是不是在求我不要杀他？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我……我是在求你，我从来没有这样求过别人。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你以为我会答应？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "只要你答应，我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我就随便你怎么样，你要我走，我就跟着你走，你要我到哪里，我就到哪里了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "我只有一句话想问你——你是为了你父亲来求我的，还是为了你自己？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "烧水，多烧些水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "怎么只有你们两个人，那姓陈的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他会来的，现在他大概去找女人去了，这地方中看的女人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "今天明明是杀人的天气，为什么偏偏有人在这里杀猪？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "杀猪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "若不是杀猪，要这么烫的水干啥？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "听说生孩子也要用烫水的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "奇怪，这孩子一生下来，怎么就有这么大了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "莫非是怪胎？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一定是怪胎。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "原来是要命的丁姑娘。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "要命这两个字多难听，你为什么不叫我那好听一点的名字？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "我本就该想到是你的，敢冒我的名字的人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "其实你的名字也不太好听，我总奇怪，为什么有人要叫你梅花鹿呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "那也许只因为他们都知道梅花鹿的角也很利，碰上它的人就得死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "那么你就该叫大水牛才对，牛角岂非更厉害？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你大哥好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他一向很好，何况最近又赢来了一口好剑，是跟南海来的飞鲸剑客比剑赢来的，你知道他最喜欢的就是好剑了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你二哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他当然也很好，最近又把河北'虎风堂'打得稀烂，还把那三条老虎的脑袋割了下来，你知道他最喜欢的就是杀强盗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你三哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "最好的还是他，他和姑苏的南宫兄弟斗了三天，先斗唱、斗棋，再斗掌、斗剑，终于把'南宫世家'藏的三十坛陈年女儿红全赢了过来，还加上一班清吟小唱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "丁三少最喜欢的就是醇酒美人，你总该也知道的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你姐夫喜欢的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "我姐夫喜欢的当然是我姐姐。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你有多少姐姐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "不多，只有六个。你难道没听说过丁家的三剑客，七仙女？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "很好是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "我的意思就是说，幸好丁家的女人多，男人少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "那又怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你知道我一向不喜欢杀女人的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "只杀三个人幸好不多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你是不是准备去杀我三个哥哥？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你是不是只有三个哥哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "很不好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "很不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他们不在这里，当然很不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "他们若在这里呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他们只要有一个人在这里，你现在就已经是条死鹿了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你现在总该已看出他是个怎么样的人了吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "他的确是个聪明人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "聪明人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "聪明人都知道用嘴吃花生要比用嘴争吵愉快得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "我现在才知道原来女人也一样喜欢看男人洗澡的，否则为什么她还不肯走？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我们走。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你的手疼不疼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不疼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "我的手为什么会很疼呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为你是个混蛋，该说的话从来不说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "不该说的话，我也一样从来就不说的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道我要你说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "说什么也没有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么没有用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "因为路小佳已知道我们是故意想去激怒他的，也知道在这种时候绝不能发怒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你怎么知道他知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "因为他若不知道，用不着等到现在，早巳变成条死鹿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你好像很佩服他。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "但最佩服的却不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "是我自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我倒看不出你有哪点值得佩服的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "至少有一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "别人用指甲掐我的时候，我居然好像不知道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "人怎么还没有来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你们要我杀的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "他会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "他一个人来还不够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "还要一个什么人来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "我也正想去找陈大倌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "也许他永远不会来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "别人都说你是粮食店的掌柜，你真的是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "当然……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "但是我越看你越不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我总觉得你们根本不必请我来。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你们以前要杀人时，岂非总是自己杀的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "我们是请你来杀人的，并没有请你来盘问我们的底细。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "有道理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你开的价钱，我们已付给了你，也没有人间过你的底细。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "text": "可是我要的女人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡掌柜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "女人……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "那就得看你要的是哪种女人了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你是在问我想要哪种女人？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "我要的正是你这种女人，你自己一定也知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "那么你要的女人现在已有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "是我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你以为我在骗你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你当然不会骗我，只不过我总觉得你至少也该先对我笑一笑的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你还不满意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "因为我一向不喜欢笑起来像哭的女人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "我笑得虽然不好，但别的事却做得很好。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你会做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你要我做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你知不知道这是做什么用的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "这是擦背的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "我还有句话要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "我也不喜欢多话的女人，但这次却可以破例让你问一问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "text": "你的女人现在已有了，你要杀的人现在还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你不想让他活着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你来，就是为了要我杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "路小佳",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你放心，我保证他一定活不长的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    }
  ],
